laboratory_examinations.findings: Elevated creatinine at 230 mmol/L (previously 119 mmol/L 2 months prior).
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Increased from 119 mmol/L to 230 mmol/L over 2 months; normalized within 48 hours after withdrawal of NSAIDs; transient rise after ketorolac administration.

laboratory_examinations.findings: Increased uptake in L5/S1; incidental finding of diffuse bilateral increased renal uptake.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Resolution of the increased renal uptake noted on repeat bone scan after cessation of NSAIDs.
